          </li>
          <li>
            <span className="font-semibold">Full sun and heavy foot traffic:</span> polyurethane is tough, glossy, and holds up to wear.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span className="font-semibold">Need fast, simple application:</span> acrylic dries quickly and looks clean.
